    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I appreciate the kind words, but what connections am I really holding onto? Everyone has their own lives to live, and I'm just this shadow in the corner. It feels like I don't have any control left over anything... not my health, not my loneliness. I'm just at the mercy of whatever slow decline comes next. I wish I could just decide when it's time instead of just waiting to be forced.",
